2. The advertisement transaction executing method of claim 1, further comprising the steps of:
receiving and storing the advertisement information from the advertiser; and
updating the advertisement information when required by the advertiser;
wherein the advertisement information includes desirable conditions for the advertisement space as defined by the advertiser;
wherein the set of rules includes a desirable conditions rule in which the advertisement space satisfies the desirable conditions of the advertisement information.
